			<div class="separator-img"><img src="https://tecnovedadesweb.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/linea.png"  width="290" height="58" alt=""></div>
			<div>
				<p>Entendemos que la motivación principal de nuestros clientes es VENDER, por ello vamos directo al grano y te ayudamos a destacar ante tu competencia mediante una </p>
            	<p style="font-weight:bold">Página web profesional.</p>
            	<p>Que te permitirá mostrar tus productos y servicios de manera eficaz, manejar ofertas y promociones, y lograr que tus clientes compren de manera sencilla a través de los diferentes medios de pago o ponerse en contacto contigo para poder requerir tus servicios de manera efectiva.</p>
			</div>
		</ImageBanner>
	</main>
	
</Layout>
<script>
	let el = document.querySelector("#circle-animated");
	setInterval(()=>{
		if(el){
			if(el.className === "animated-circled-dash")
				el.className =  "animated-circled-hide"
			else
				el.className = "animated-circled-dash"
		}	
	},4000);
</script>
<style>	
main{	
	display: flex;	
	justify-content: center;
	flex-direction: column;	
	align-items: center;
	section{
		width: 70%;
		height: 750px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;		
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
		h1{
			color: var(--fg-color-1);			
		}
	}
}
h3{	
	letter-spacing: -0.5px;
	text-transform: uppercase;	
	margin: 20px auto;	
	& > h1{
		color: var(--fg-color-1);		
	}
}
span{
	font-size: inherit;
	color: yellow;
	position: relative;
	& > svg{
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		width: calc(100% + 20px);
		height: calc(100% + 20px);
		transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 40px;
	}
}
#circle-animated{
	fill: none;
	stroke: #FF5A00;
	
	font-weight: 600;
	stroke-width: 9px;
}
.divider{
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
	height: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 20px;		
	padding: 20px;
	& > span{			
		height: 100%;
		width: 3rem;
		background-color: white;
	}
}
button{
	width: 14rem;
	font-size: 17px;
	letter-spacing: 0.2px;
	font-family: var(--primary-font-condessed);
	text-align: center;
	font-weight: 500;
	font-stretch: 20%;
	line-height: 1;
	word-spacing: 0px;
	padding: 14px 0px;
	background-color: var(--fg-color-3);
	border-radius: 10px;
	color: var(--fg-color-1);
	border: 0px;	
	animation: scaleButton ;	
	animation-duration: 0.8s;	
	animation-timing-function: linear;
	animation-iteration-count: infinite;
	animation-play-state: paused;
	&:hover{
		animation-play-state: running;
		background-color: var(--fg-color-1);
		color: #0069FF;
	}
}
@keyframes scaleButton{
	25%{
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}
	75%{
		transform: scale(0.9);
	}
}
.separator-img{
	padding: 20px 0px;
	img{
		width: 28%;
		height: auto;
	}
}
.sub-tittle-container{
	padding: 50px 0px;
	& > h3{
		color: var(--fg-color-1);
		font-size: var(--size-large);
	}
	
}
.animated-circled-dash{
	& > svg > path{
		animation: head-circle-dash;
		animation-duration: 1.2s;
		animation-iteration-count: 1;
	}
	
}
.animated-circled-hide{
	& > svg > path{
		opacity: 1;
		stroke-dasharray: 1500 1500;	
		animation: hide-highlight .4s forwards;
		animation-iteration-count: 1;
	}

}
@keyframes hide-highlight {
    0% {
        opacity: 1;
        stroke-dasharray: 1500 1500
    }

    to {
        opacity: 0;
        filter: blur(10px)
    }
}
@keyframes head-circle-dash{
	0%{
		stroke-dasharray: 0 1500;
		opacity: 1;		
	}
	100%{
		stroke-dasharray: 1500 1500;
		opacity: 1;
	}
}
</style>
